Other measurements

Compare width with depth - height with your space

For proper placement, measure your room and ensure you have at least 30 inches of walking space in front of the sofa.

What do these measurements mean?

Width

The total width from arm to arm (the first measurement in the series)

Depth

The measurement from front to back (the second measurement in the series)

Height

The total height from floor to the top of the backrest (the third measurement)

reviews.name: Isabella White
reviews.text: I've been using this sofa for a month now, and it still feels brand new. The fabric is soft, yet durable, and the color hasn't faded. It's a perfect size for my living room, and I've received many compliments from guests. Absolutely a must-have if you're looking for comfort and style.
reviews.title: Stylish and Functional
